social_posts.post_text: I am so unbelievably proud of this man. I am so excited to move on to this next chapter with you. Congratulations!
Did I mention that @tim__mccauley graduated? I love him so much it's stupid!

I have the incredibly exciting news that My Year of Dicks has made the Oscars short list for Best Animated Short. I am so grateful to have had the opportunity to be a part of this project and to help bring @pamelaribon 's amazing story to life. It will be one of the true pleasures of my life to have stepped into the shoes of her teenage self. Glad to see this film get all the love and adoration it deserves!
I can't believe it has already been 5 years since I got married to my best friend! @tim__mccauley I love you so much, here's to another 5 and then a lifetime after that. 🖤

If you had told me over a year and a half ago as I auditioned for the lead in an animated short with the funniest title I have ever heard in the guest room of my house that we would be nominated for an Oscar now I probably would have felt just as crazy as I still do today! I will never get over how much this project has changed my life. I am so grateful for all the amazing people I have worked with on this masterpiece!
My stories from the day My Year of Dicks got the Oscars Nomination!
If they watched Prom Night they'd save time. There's a formula to it. A very simple formula! EVERYBODY'S A SUSPECT!

This goober turns 20 today and I refuse to believe that is true. You will always be a little baby to me even if I am blown away by the amazing man you have grown into. Happy birthday to my little guy. Love you stinky!

Finally doing an Oscars 2023 photo dump! This day was so incredibly surreal for me. I am so grateful to have been a part of the @myyearofdicks team. All of these amazing women have taught me so much and inspired me beyond belief!

I cannot believe that this baby is turning 18 today. Dylan you are one of the funniest people I know being around you is hard to breathe because I am laughing so hard. I am so proud of the man you have grown into and cannot wait to see what else there is to come. You are so smart and loving and I know you are going to do great things. HAPPY BIRTHDAY!
An angel who did not so much fall just sauntered vaguely downward.
Happy Halloween.
1 month. 12 costumes. (part 1)
1 month. 12 costumes. (part 2)
1 month. 12 costumes. (part 3)
@matthewlillard is one of the nicest people I have had the pleasure of meeting and I’m so glad @jessica_rogari and I got to meet the original Ghost Face killers! Ft: my beautiful amazing mom!!!
It’s a SCREAM baby!
I have the prettiest friends!
Nothing quite like being back with my family for Christmas.

2023 had some on the highest and lowest points of my life, but the highs were absolutely insane. I still can’t believe I was at the Oscar’s this year with the amazing MYOD team! This year might have kicked my ass but I’m hoping it has set me up for many amazing years to come. Thank you to my loving family and all my fantastic friends I don’t think I could have made it through this year without you all.
